#Text=Good evening everybody and welcome to Beyond the Mat !
#Text=The Beyond the Mat show after WrestleMania .
#Text=Well , it happened folks .
#Text=WrestleMania happened , Raw happened , Smackdown happened , everything fucking happened .
#Text=Holy shit , there is so much to talk about this week , and we ’re going to cover it all , the best we can .
#Text=I ’m your host as always , Dave , and I am joined by Alex .
#Text=Howdy !
#Text=We were supposed to have word from Carl .
#Text=We do n’t know where he is , so I ’ll just take that as a – he ’s one of the people that is cutting his wrists because the Undertaker ’s career is over !
#Text=Those of you who take offense to that , fuck off and –
#Text=What did , uh , what ’s his name – what did , uh , our , our , wh- , the one that always is dressed up like Undertaker on Facebook ?
#Text=Yeah , he did the exact same thing , he folded his clothes and put ’em on or something .
#Text=Yeah , I thought I saw that picture , what does it look like , what is he – what is he doing ?
#Text=I ’m ignoring anybody who is taking this retirement personally and acting like this is the end of the fucking world .
#Text=Um , I ’m gon na say this right now , and I ’m gon na say it again when we get to the match – I ’m glad it ’s over .
#Text=And I know people that are getting offended by that .
#Text=I ’m glad it ’s over .
#Text=Look , I I can just – look , I fucking cried when – I fucking cried when – but it ’s OK , it ’s it ’s not the end of the world .
#Text=It ’s not the end of the world .
#Text=You can still watch wrestling , it ’s not “ oh , he retired ; that ’s it , I ’m done , I ca n’t watch it anymore . ”
#Text=I mean , for God ’s sakes , he was only there like –
#Text=I mean , how many days are in a year ?
#Text=365 days , so he was there one out of – c’m on .
#Text=Three days .
#Text=Four days .
#Text=He made two appearances .
#Text=I mean , I mean , OK , think about it like this : at Wrestlemania 31 he was there once the whole year , cause he was only there the day of Wrestlemania .
#Text=So that ’s one day of the year that you watched him , that year .
#Text=So that ’s , really ?
#Text=Are you really missing that much of wrestling by not having Undertaker there ?
#Text=I mean , come on .
#Text=He ’s my favorite wrestler , easily .
#Text=Yeah , and he ’ll be mine as well , but there does come a time when you have to go “ look , it ’s over ” .
#Text=I mean the guy – the guy – the guy ca n’t wrestle forever .
#Text=I mean he ’s – he was , 53 ?
#Text=Yeah that was not -- he wrestled like a 75,000 year - old man .
#Text=Yeah , when we get to that match I ’m gon na be so critical on it .
#Text=And I know people are gon na be pissed off at me .
#Text=And I do n’t care , I ’m gon na call it like I see it , the rose colored glasses are off , the nostalgia is gone .
#Text=Stop wanting the fucking 90s back , because the 90s are dead , get the fuck over it .
#Text=Um , yeah .
#Text=You people and your fucking 90s nostalgia , stop it .
#Text=Let the 90s fucking die .
#Text=Let it fucking die , please , just stop .
#Text=Stop .
#Text=Ugh .
#Text=How ’s your week been Alex ?
#Text=It ’s been good , yeah .
#Text=Um , it was – like , I do n’t even remember – well , let me see .
#Text=I forgot to mention , I guess I should mention this now .
#Text=Ugh !
#Text=Good time , better than never .
#Text=This is actually not from this week but , let me see .
#Text=When was this ?
#Text=Let me look at the calendar real quick on the computer .
#Text=This would have been … not last week , but the week – no , not last week , not the week before that , but the week before that , on March 25th was my 29th birthday .
#Text=And you ’re just now letting us know ?
#Text=Well I belie- I think I was wished happy birthday by all of you on Facebook , so , that ’s fine .
#Text=But I did n’t – but I do n’t think we ’ve had a show since , cause we – cause we – cause we missed so many shows in a row .
#Text=But uh , yeah , I put a video up on YouTube .
#Text=We all drank a whole lot ta shit .
#Text=Um , I did n’t get drunk at all despite literally shotgunning I think six or seven shots of … was it tequila ? .. yeah , I think it was like really really decent tequila , in a row .
#Text=I did n’t feel anything , cause I do n’t know that ’s just how I am .
#Text=And some sake .
#Text=But yeah , that ’s up there on my YouTube channel , not that anybody ever goes on it .
#Text=So uh , this week I do n’t know , they added more DLC , the only DLC for King of Fighters .
#Text=King of Fighters XIV .
#Text=Did you say you liked Rock Howard ?
#Text=I forget .
#Text=I do n’t mind Rock Howard .
#Text=Um I think he ’s cool .
#Text=I ’ve always been an Andy Bogard , Terry Bogard …
#Text=Well they ’re already in the game , so .
#Text=Yeah , I know .
#Text=And I ’m decent with Kim but I ’m OK with Rock .
#Text=Rock is now DLC for the game along with uh who else ?
#Text=Yamazaki .
#Text=Is Iori in there or did they take him out ?
#Text=It ’s Iori I think , or Yori ?
#Text=Tall guy with the fucking red hair .
#Text=Not Rugal , but …
#Text=No , I know who Rugal is .
